originalText.text: I am very happy with the web design work Mark and his team at Bionic Egg did for our cosmetic start up. They go above and beyond for their clients. They produce a great product for you with great support and great service. Mark really cares about what you want and makes sure you are comfortable during the entire process. Very easy to work with and very reasonable pricing. I am so happy we chose Bionic Egg for our web site and SEO. Highly recommended!

originalText.text:
If I could give Mark 6 stars, I absolutely would.  With an exceptional eye for design and genuine care his projects/tasks, few can compare to his level of expertise.

While many companies rely on lack of knowledge to draw new consumers, BIONIC EGG is the ultimate honest resource.

Businesses like this are few and far between.  Through his unwavering honesty and integrity, Mark allows companies the freedom to make business decisions that are ACTUALLY what’s best for them. In this way, he stands apart from MOST  branding companies.

Mark is timely and meticulous, kind and sensible, skillful, and ALWAYS delivers on his word.  I am happy to have had the pleasure of working closely with Mark-a true team player. With our new project, I know our business is sure success.

Mark genuinely has a passion for what he does and it shows. Partnering with Bionic Egg will allow your company to simply, be the best. I would 100% recommend him to anyone looking to take their brand to the next level.

Our office can not thank you enough!

originalText.text: I don't write reviews often. I can't say enough about Mark and his attention to detail and follow through.  I have used Bionic Egg for both my startup dental product company which Mark did the complete branding package, including name creation,  logo, website design, and build my e commerce platform. Mark also helped me file and get trademarks for the names we created, at a fraction of the cost I have experienced in the past hiring legal firms.  For my dental practice, Mark helped get my website current and he also increased my visibility on Google. My new patients have increased almost 30% after switching to Bionic.  Mark, bravo! You are truly the best in the industry.
